OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPolice forces told to vet  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fstaff after Carrick case   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, All police forces will be asked to     
OL,6, check staff against national databases 
OL,7, to identify if anyone "slipped through 
OL,8, the net", the Home Office says.        
OL,10,FIt follows the case of David Carrick   
OL,11,Fwho admitted dozens of rape and sexual 
OL,12,Foffences as a Met Police officer.      
OL,14,FThe National Police Chiefs Council     
OL,15,F(NPCC) will ask forces to check current
OL,16,Fstaff recruited before tougher vetting 
OL,17,Fof recruits was introduced in 2006..   
OL,19,FThe College of Policing will also be   
OL,20,Fasked to strengthen vetting procedures.
